title: Uncle Malaria - Cannabis Soundscapes (2003)
description:
An Ambient album made back in 2003 by Uncle Malaria, but due to lack of computer power, was not able to mixdown until now... For some reason he wanted a single 40 minute track....
This album is a series of evolving soundscapes made to fall asleep to. It was inspired by SAW 85-92 and SAW II by Aphex Twin.

01 - Northern Lights 10:18
02 - Kush 5:04
03 - G-13 5:51
04 - White Widow 6:31
05 - Panama Red 8:39
06 - Cannabis Sativa 7:08

All songs were mixed down from 32bit wav files to 320kbs cbr mp3s.
Originally made with Cool Edit Pro 2.0, Reason, and Rebirth.  Resequenced and Mixed in 2008 with Adobe Audition 3.0.
